title: Did Stuart Minkos become Chanel West Coast?
subtitle: Lee Norris, known as Corey Matthews, the geek of the Stuart Menkos middle school in Boy Meets the World, did not become Chanel's actress West Coast.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: The actor who played Stuart Minkos on the TV show "Boy Meets the World" became Chanel West Coast.
